article_id:1376,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Connection Issues in Co-op [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1591754400"></span>]</strong></span><br>We have confirmed that the co-op connection issues have been resolved.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send out 150 wyrmite to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1591754400"></span>.<br><br>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><hr><div>We have confirmed that connection issues can prevent players from playing co-op quests.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue. Any updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1591743600,update_time1591754646